NovaArch Live Environment
-------------------------
Gaming + daily-use focused Arch-based custom ISO.

Live boots as user live with no tty login prompt — use NovaArch Welcome → Launch Installer (archinstall wizard) after Wi‑Fi works.

Multi-monitor (Hyprland): Super+[ / Super+] = focus prev/next screen; Super+Shift+[ / ] moves the workspace.

GTK theme (no gsettings on Hyprland): run lxappearance or Welcome → Theme tab.

Useful commands:
  archinstall / novaarch-launch-installer
  novaarch-create-user (optional helper)
  novaarch-web-wallpaper
  nmtui
  steam
  mullvad-vpn
  piper
